OL,4,Ctakes root
OL,6,FAnd while he's not actually tiptoeing
OL,7,Fthrough the tulips, Infrastructure
OL,8,FMinister John O'Dowd is backing the
OL,9,F'No Mow May' initiative.
OL,11,F"Road safety will be our priority and
OL,12,Fwe will continue to cut (road) sight
OL,13,Flines," he said.
OL,15,F"But as a department that owns quite a
OL,16,Fsignificant amount of land, I felt it
OL,17,Fwas only right that we joined 'No Mow
OL,18,FMay'.
