OL,6,F"At its core is protecting our
OL,7,Fenvironment, promoting biodiversity,
OL,8,Fand allowing through that, wildflowers
OL,9,Fand colourful flora to flourish along
OL,10,Four roadside verges. Causeway Coast
OL,11,Fand Glens Council is an example of how
OL,12,Fwe can do this."
OL,14,FThe minister added: "They've been
OL,15,Fworking in partnership with my
OL,16,Fdepartment for several years, and I
OL,17,Fvisited the area today to formally
OL,18,Fcongratulate them on their work, but
OL,19,Falso to continue to learn how we can
OL,20,Fdo it better."
