OL,6,FLeaving the mower in the shed a little
OL,7,Flonger will provide a feast for hungry
OL,8,Fpollinators, birds and insects as the
OL,9,Fwildflowers grow.
OL,11,FRobbie also recommends building a bug
OL,12,Fhotel by placing old hewn logs or old
OL,13,Fwood in a section of the garden and
OL,14,Fencouraging insects to nest there.
OL,16,F"That's a great way of getting the
OL,17,Fchildren involved in helping the
OL,18,Fenvironment too," he says.
